<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; visibility: visible; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">为推进班团一体化建设，</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; visibility: visible; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">凝聚班级向心力，</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; visibility: visible; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">强化班级（团支书和班长）在学生管理工作中的主体地位，</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; visibility: visible; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">发挥先进典型的示范作用，</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; visibility: visible; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">助力广大同学成长成才，</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; visibility: visible; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">经济管理学院决定于本学期开展</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; visibility: visible; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">“筑梦青春’经‘彩纷呈”班团建设主题。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 24px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">宝子们，让我们来欣赏一下经管班级的风采吧</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: cen